page.title: 06HOME LIFE,LIFE STYLES ADULT
page.content: MY NAME IS JEANETTE GODDEN. I AM MARRIED TO CEDRIC A BUILDER,WE HAVE TWO CHILDREN,MARK 15AND CLAIRE 11. WE HAVE A THREE BEDROOMED BUNGALOW, WITH LOUNGE,DINING ROOM,KITCHEN, OFFICE,HALL AND BATHROOM. WE HAVE ONE ACRE OF ORCHARD AND BUILDER'S YARD,AN ACRE OF GARDEN LAID OUT TO LAWNS,FRUIT AND VEGETABLES,A GREEN HOUSE AND SWIMMING POOL. WE OWN AN ESTATE CAR AND TWO TRUCKS. OUR BUNGALOW IS SOLID FUEL CENTRAL HEATED AND DOUBLE GLAZED. WE HAVE 2 TELEVISIONS,VIDEO,WASHING MACHINE, FREEZER,FRIDGE AND COOKER. TYPICAL DAY.UP7.00,BREAKFAST CEREAL AND TOAST,12.30 LUNCH-SANDWICHES,6.30 DINNER,MEAT AND 3 VEG.SWEET.HOT MILK BEDTIME,10.00TO10.30.
